Fidel FLAMINI and Beatriz Flamini, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
BANK UNITED, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1883 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 01, 2018
